          <source>Click the <ph id="ph1">![</ph>Lightbulb<ph id="ph2">](images/bulb.png)</ph> icon which appears in the left margin and select <bpt id="p1">**</bpt>Convert to Raw String Literal<ept id="p1">**</ept> from the context menu.</source>
